Comment: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:28.87,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(100,150)\3c&H000000&}bear witness to my song
Comment: 0,0:02:28.87,0:02:33.37,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(100,150)\3c&H000000&}Your heart contains all its truth
Comment: 0,0:02:33.37,0:02:36.42,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(100,150)\3c&H000000&}Even when all you see in your path are storms
